proxy:
To use a proxy with mineflayer, add the key `connect` to your `mineflayer.createBot()` like this:
```diff
const bot = mineflayer.createBot({
+  connect: (client) => {
+    socks.createConnection({
+      proxy: {
+        host: <proxy_ip/proxy_host>,
+        port: <myProxyPort>,'
+        type: 5,
+        userId: '<proxy_username>',
+        password: '<proxy_password>'
+      },
+      command: 'connect',
+      destination: {
+        host: '<mc_server_host/ip>',
+        port: <mc_server_port>
+      }
+    }, (err, info) => {
+      if (err) {
+        console.log(err)
+        return
+      }
+      client.setSocket(info.socket)
+      client.emit('connect')
+    })
+  },
- host: 'localhost'
  username: <mc_username>,
  password: <mc_password>
})
```
